If a RAM is 32-bit addressable, it has total byte addresses as below.

    0x00000000 -   0xFFFFFFFF

    (0)        -   4294967295 

Means, this RAM has 4294967296 bytes available in total.

In paging whole RAM (whether its 32-bit addressable, or 64-bit addressable),is
divided into slots of same size.

This slot of same size is called a PAGE. 

Generally (in many OS), this the SIZE of each PAGE is 4096 bytes (4 KB).

So, How many PAGES can be present in a 32-bit addressable RAM?

    Max number of bytes available in a 32-bit addressable RAM : 4294967296 bytes
    PAGE size                                                 : 4096 bytes

        Total pages = 4294967296 / 4096 = 1048576 pages.

Hence, we have total 1048576 pages in a 32-bit addressable RAM when the size of
each page is 4096 bytes.

We can represent this RAM as below:

            ----------------------- <--- 0x00000000
            |                     |
            |       PAGE 1        |
            | (size : 4096 bytes  |
            |                     |
            ----------------------- <--- 0x00001000
            |                     |
            |       PAGE 2        |
            | (size : 4096 bytes  |
            |                     |
            ----------------------- <--- 0x00002000
            |                     |
            |       PAGE 3        |
            | (size : 4096 bytes  |
            |                     |
            ----------------------- <--- 0x00003000
            |                     |
            |       PAGE 4        |
            | (size : 4096 bytes  |
            |                     |
            ----------------------- <--- 0x00004000
            |                     |
            |       PAGE 5        |
            | (size : 4096 bytes  |
            |                     |
            ----------------------- <--- 0x00005000
            |                     |
            |       PAGE 6        |
            | (size : 4096 bytes  |
            |                     |
            ----------------------- <--- 0x00006000
            |                     |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |        |            |
            |       \|/           |
            |                     |
            |                     |
            ----------------------- <---- 0xFFFFEFFF
            |                     |
            |     PAGE 1048576    |
            | (size : 4096 bytes  |
            |                     |
            ----------------------- <---- 0xFFFFFFFF

